# Chrome Web Store API Credentials
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Copy this file to .cws-credentials and fill in your values.
# NEVER commit .cws-credentials — it's in .gitignore.
#
# Full setup guide: https://developer.chrome.com/docs/webstore/using-api
#
# ── Step 1: Enable the API ──────────────────────────────────
#   Go to https://console.developers.google.com
#   Create or select a project → search "Chrome Web Store API" → Enable
#
# ── Step 2: Create OAuth credentials ────────────────────────
#   OAuth consent screen → External → fill required fields
#   Add your Google account email as a test user
#   Credentials → Create Credentials → OAuth client ID → Web application
#   Add authorized redirect URI: https://developers.google.com/oauthplayground
#   Save → copy your Client ID and Client Secret below
#
# ── Step 3: Get a refresh token ─────────────────────────────
#   Go to https://developers.google.com/oauthplayground
#   Click gear icon (⚙) → check "Use your own OAuth credentials"
#   Enter your Client ID and Client Secret
#   In Step 1 (left panel), type this scope and click Authorize:
#     https://www.googleapis.com/auth/chromewebstore
#   Sign in with your Chrome Web Store developer account
#   Click "Exchange authorization code for tokens"
#   Copy the refresh_token below
#
# ── Step 4: Find your Publisher ID ──────────────────────────
#   Go to https://chrome.google.com/webstore/devconsole
#   Click Account (left sidebar) → your Publisher ID is shown there
#
# ── Step 5: Find your Extension IDs ─────────────────────────
#   In the Developer Dashboard, click each extension
#   The extension ID is in the URL or on the extension detail page
#   e.g. https://chrome.google.com/webstore/devconsole/.../items/<EXTENSION_ID>
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

CWS_CLIENT_ID=""
CWS_CLIENT_SECRET=""
CWS_REFRESH_TOKEN=""
CWS_PUBLISHER_ID=""

# Extension IDs — one per extension
# Variable name format: CWS_ID_<ExtName> (hyphens become underscores)
CWS_ID_GrokExt_opalite=""
CWS_ID_GeminiExt_opalite=""
CWS_ID_ChatGPTExt_opalite=""
CWS_ID_da_stash_helper=""
CWS_ID_InstagramExt=""
